title: 2016 AFL Mark of the Year
text: The <a href="Australian%20Football%20League">Australian Football League</a> celebrates the best <a href="Mark%20%28Australian%20football%29">mark</a> of the season through the annual <a href="Mark%20of%20the%20Year">Mark of the Year</a> competition. Each round three marks are nominated and fans are able to vote online for their favourite. <a href="Majak%20Daw">Majak Daw</a> of the <a href="North%20Melbourne%20Football%20Club">North Melbourne Football Club</a> for his mark taken in round 18 against the <a href="Collingwood%20Football%20Club">Collingwood Football Club</a>.
